  "title": "Freight Forwarding Co-ordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job description</strong></p><ol><li>Coordinate the logistics of inbound and outbound cargo, including booking shipments, arranging transportation, and tracking deliveries</li><li>Liaise with internal teams, external carriers, and customers to provide updates and resolve any issues that may arise</li><li>Maintain accurate and up-to-date records and documentation related to all logistics activities</li><li>Assist in the preparation of reports and analysis to identify areas for process improvement</li><li>Support the implementation of new logistics initiatives and technologies to enhance operational efficiency</li></ol><p><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p><ol><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in a logistics or freight forwarding role.</li><li>Strong organisational and time management skills, with the ability to prioritise and multitask effectively</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to liaise with a diverse range of stakeholders</li><li>Proficient in using logistics management software and MS Office applications</li><li>Knowledge of freight forwarding processes, customs regulations, and supply chain management principles</li><li>A problem-solving mindset and a commitment to continuous improvement</li></ol>",
